parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the body and peeling of paint can lead to rusting of the aluminum hood and tailgate, causing structural damage and compromising the vehicle's safety.
symptoms: Paint bubbling and peeling on the hood and tailgate
rusting of the aluminum body panels
corrosion of the bracket that holds the hood down
and water collecting in the doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the interior door handle can cause occupants to become trapped inside the vehicle, leading to potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Interior door handle breaking off or fracturing
making it difficult or impossible to exit the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water leaks can cause electrical issues, leading to malfunctions of various vehicle systems, including the brake system, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Water entering the vents and coming through the roof
water collecting in the doors
and issues with the brake system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic deploying running boards can cause occupants to fall while exiting or entering the vehicle, leading to injuries.
symptoms: Running board failing to deploy
causing occupants to fall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brake pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brake pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The ABS light illuminates
the traction control light illuminates
the vehicle shakes or vibrates when braking
the vehicle is difficult to control when braking
the vehicle loses traction when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to jerk, hesitate, or fail to shift gears, leading to loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: Abnormal noise from the transmission
difficulty shifting gears
hesitation
jerking
or failure to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rollaway accidents can cause damage to property, injury, or even death, especially if the vehicle is on an incline or in a confined space.
symptoms: Vehicle rolls away without warning
even when parked on a level surface
and can cause damage to surrounding objects or other vehicles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the brake light switch can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: Brake lights do not function
or the vehicle is unable to shift into gear due to the faulty brake light switch.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the window and door motors can cause inconvenience, discomfort, and even safety risks if the windows or doors become stuck.
symptoms: Windows or doors fail to open or close
or become stuck in a particular position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the 4WD system can cause loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver, especially in off-road or low-traction conditions.
symptoms: Loud clanking sound
twisted driveshaft
or failure of the 4WD system to engage or disengage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the retractable running board can cause injury or entrapment, especially if it retracts unexpectedly.
symptoms: Retractable running board retracts unexpectedly
causing injury or entrapment.
